{"_path":"/crypto/post_knbnkqf-en","_dir":"crypto","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Arbitrum DAO Approves $23.4 Million for Gaming Projects","description":"The Arbitrum network DAO has officially approved the creation of a $23.4 million gaming fund aimed at developing blockchain games on the Layer 2 network. The proposal received overwhelming community support and represents one of the largest targeted investments in the gaming industry within the Layer 2 space.","lead":"Arbitrum launches its largest gaming fund to develop blockchain games","rubric":"crypto","tags":["news","cryptocenter"],"author":"Editorial","date":"2025-07-09","cover":"/imported/post_knbnkqf/cover.webp","translation":true,"lang":"en","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Arbitrum"}]},{"type":"text","value":" network DAO has officially approved the creation of a "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"$23.4 million"}]},{"type":"text","value":" gaming fund aimed at developing blockchain games on the Layer 2 network. The proposal received overwhelming community support and represents one of the largest targeted investments in the gaming industry within the Layer 2 space."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"structure-of-the-gaming-catalyst-program"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Structure of the Gaming Catalyst Program"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gaming Catalyst Program (GCP)"}]},{"type":"text","value":" will distribute funds over 18 months through a grant system focused on:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"chi